"el_underlineAction\">採用情報</span><span class=\"icon\"></span></button>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"item_body\">\r\n              <div class=\"item_body_inner ct_std\">\r\n                <div>\r\n                  <div class=\"item_body_head\">\r\n                    <h2 class=\"item_body_hdg\"><a class=\"el_circleArrowLink\" href=\"/recruit.html\"><span class=\"el_circleArrowLink_txt el_underlineAction\">採用情報<span class=\"hp_smHeaderOnly\"> トップ</span></span><span class=\"el_circleArrow\"><span class=\"el_arrow\"></span></span></a>\r\n                    </h2>\r\n                    <button class=\"closeBtn hp_lgHeaderOnly\" type=\"button\">閉じる<span class=\"icon\"></span></button>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"item_body_body\">\r\n                    <section>\r\n                      <ul class=\"linkList\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"/recruit_fresh.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span class=\"el_underlineAction\">新卒採用サイト</span><span class=\"el_circleArrow el_circleArrow__white hp_lgHeaderOnly\"><span class=\"el_arrow\"></span></span></a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"/recruit.html\"><span class=\"el_underlineAction\">キャリア採用</span><span class=\"el_circleArrow el_circleArrow__white hp_lgHeaderOnly\"><span class=\"el_arrow\"></span></span></a></li>\r\n                      </ul>\r\n                    </section>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <div class=\"hp_smHeaderOnly\">\r\n          <ul class=\"linkBtnList\">\r\n            <li><a class=\"contact\" href=\"/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\r\n            <li><a class=\"mat\" href=\"/download/\">資料ダウンロード</a></li>\r\n          </ul><a class=\"globalLink\" href=\"https://www.cmp-chugoku.com/\">Global</a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </nav>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"ly_header_overlay hp_lgHeaderOnly\" id=\"ly_header_overlay\"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n</div><div id=\"areaWrapper1\" class=\"pbAreaWrapper1\"><div id=\"areaWrapper2\" class=\"pbAreaWrapper2\"><div id=\"mainArea\" class=\"pbMainArea\">\n\t<div id=\"area0\" class=\"pbArea \">\n\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_fvWrapper pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820336\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvWithBg pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820337\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvWithBg_imgBox pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820325\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div><img src=\"/recruit/img/mv.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvWithBg_inner c_ct_std pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820338\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvWithBg_enTxt pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820322\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<p lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">recruit</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvWithBg_title pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820324\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<h2>採用情報</h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvWithBg_lead pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820323\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<p>漕ぎ出せ、世界へ、未来へ。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_breadcrumb c_ct_std pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820339\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"  pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820345\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1794533\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<nav class=\"bl_breadcrumb\"><ol><li><a href=\"/\"><span>HOME</span></a></li><li><span>採用情報</span></li></ol></nav>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvNoImg_copy c_ct_std pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820334\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<p>ー 目指すはサステナブルで高収益なグローバル・ニッチ・トップ企業 ー</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_fvNoImg_body c_ct_std pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820333\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<p>当社の目指す姿を実現するためには、多様な価値観を持った人財一人ひとりが主役となり力を発揮することが必要不可欠と考えています。<br />\n「やってみたい」という気持ちを尊重し、ビジョンを叶えることができる会社です。<br />\nグローバルなフィールドで個性を発揮しながら共に成長し、可能性を広げていきませんか。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"c_ct_std cmp_areaWrapper pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820340\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_contSet pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820341\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_el_hdgLg pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820330\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<h2>新卒採用</h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_el_hdgMd pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820332\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<h3>無限の可能性を秘めた塗料と、あなたの未来を一緒に探していきませんか。</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820331\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<p>当社には、100年以上にわたり磨き続けてきた確かな技術力と、時代や環境によって異なる様々な課題をお客様と試行錯誤し、解決してきた提案力があります。社会を支える技術ほど日常に溶け込み、その価値は気づきにくいもの。それでも私たちはこれまでも、これからも、一人ひとりの意志やアイデアが未来の当たり前を塗り替えていく。そう信じて無限の可能性を一緒に実現していく仲間を求めています。下記リンク先の新卒採用サイトをご覧ください。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_bl_recruitSiteBanner-Wrapper pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820342\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820346\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_recruitSiteBanner\">\r\n  <a class=\"bl_recruitSiteBanner_frame\" href=\"/recruit-fresh.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n    <div class=\"bl_recruitSiteBanner_head\">\r\n      <hgroup class=\"el_hGroup el_hGroup__lg\">\r\n        <p class=\"el_hGroup_enTxt\" lang=\"en\">RECRUITMENT SITE</p>\r\n        <h2 class=\"el_hGroup_hdg\">新卒採用サイト</h2>\r\n      </hgroup>\r\n      <div class=\"circleBlank\"></div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"bl_recruitSiteBanner_bg\">\r\n      <div class=\"hp_spNone\">\r\n        <img src=\"/assets/img/common/bl_recruitSiteBanner/bl_recruitSiteBanner_bg_img_01.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"387\" height=\"420\" loading=\"lazy\">\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div>\r\n        <img class=\"hp_spNone\" src=\"/assets/img/common/bl_recruitSiteBanner/bl_recruitSiteBanner_bg_img_02.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"386\" height=\"420\" loading=\"lazy\"><img class=\"hp_spOnly\" src=\"/assets/img/common/bl_recruitSiteBanner/bl_recruitSiteBanner_bg_img_02_sp.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"168\" height=\"300\" loading=\"lazy\">\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div>\r\n        <img class=\"hp_spNone\" src=\"/assets/img/common/bl_recruitSiteBanner/bl_recruitSiteBanner_bg_img_03.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"387\" height=\"420\" loading=\"lazy\"><img class=\"hp_spOnly\" src=\"/assets/img/common/bl_recruitSiteBanner/bl_recruitSiteBanner_bg_img_03_sp.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"167\" height=\"300\" loading=\"lazy\">\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </a>\r\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_newsPartsBlock pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820343\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_el_hdgLg pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820328\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<h2>キャリア採用</h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"cmp_el_hdgMd pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820326\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>\n<h2>これまでの経験やキャリアを当社で思う存分発揮しませんか。</h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820327\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbBlock pbBlockBase\">\n<div>当社では、キャリア採用を随時行っています。これまで培ってきたご経験やスキル、専門性を活かし、当社のさらなる成長をともに推進していただける方を歓迎いたします。ご興味をお持ちの方は、下記リンク先のお問い合わせフォームよりお気軽にご連絡ください。皆さまからのご応募を心よりお待ちしております。</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"linkTxts pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820344\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820347\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elLinkList\">\r\n  <a class=\"bl_arrowTxtIcon\" href=\"/contact/form-hr.html\">\r\n    <span class=\"el_circleArrow\"><span class=\"el_arrow\"></span></span>\r\n    <p class=\"el_underlineAction\">キャリア採用への応募に関するお問い合わせ</p>\r\n  </a>\r\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n</div></div></div><div id=\"footerArea\" class=\"pbFooterArea\">\n\t<div id=\"area4\" class=\"pbArea \">\n\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"  pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820352\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1794321\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ly_sideNav hp_spNone\" id=\"ly_sideNav\"><a class=\"ly_sideNav_item matBtn\" href=\"/download/\">資料ダウンロード</a>\r\n  <button class=\"ly_sideNav_item searchBtn\" type=\"button\">サイト内検索</button><a class=\"ly_sideNav_item contactBtn\" href=\"/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a>\r\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"  pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1820351\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested \" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pbNested pbNestedWrapper \"  id=\"pbBlock1794320\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ly_searchWindow\" id=\"ly_searchWindow\" hidden=\"